## Unrecoverable parsing error

```catala
declaration scope A:
  output i content integer

scope A:
  definition i equals
    # a token "all" is intentionally missing
    combine x among [ 1 ; 2 ; 3 ] in acc initially 0 with
      x + acc
```

*Some very important text*

```catala
declaration scope B:
  output i content integer
```

*Some other important text*

```catala
some invalid catala code
```

